{"word":"G4638 - σκήνωμα - skḗnōma - skay'-no-mah - Tabernacle","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σκήνωμα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">skḗnōma</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">skay'-no-mah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Tabernacle</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"கூடாரம் - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"a tent, tabernacle: of the temple as God's habitation"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4637 - σκηνόω - skēnóō - skay-no'-o/4637\">G4637</a>; an <i>encampment</i>, that is, (figuratively) the <i>Temple</i> (as God&rsquo;s residence), the <i>body</i> (as a tenement for the soul): - tabernacle.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1981/1981\">G1981</a>, <a href=\"#/G2681/2681\">G2681</a>, <a href=\"#/G4633/4633\">G4633</a>, <a href=\"#/G4634/4634\">G4634</a>, <a href=\"#/G4635/4635\">G4635</a>, <a href=\"#/G4636/4636\">G4636</a>, <a href=\"#/G4637/4637\">G4637</a>, <a href=\"#/G4638/4638\">G4638</a>"}]}